com.nokia.maps.component.feedback

Class TooltipComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nokia.maps.component.AbstractMapComponent
      • com.nokia.maps.component.feedback.TooltipComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MapComponent

    public class TooltipComponent
extends AbstractMapComponent
    This class defines a MapComponent which associates tooltip text to a MapObject. When the MapObject is moved to the centre of the screen the associated text is displayed in a tooltip. Tooltips are static text and do not respond to touch events.
